OL,3,CCompany fined more than #430,000 over
OL,4,Cforklift truck death
OL,6,FThe widow of a delivery driver who
OL,7,Fdied in a forklift truck accident has
OL,8,Fspoken of her heartbreak after his
OL,9,Femployer was fined more than #430,000.
OL,11,FChris Keegan was fatally trapped when
OL,12,Fthe forklift truck he was driving
OL,13,Ftoppled over as he reversed it onto a
OL,14,Ftrailer at Hessle Plant Ltd in
OL,15,FCastleford, West Yorkshire, in
OL,16,FNovember 2023.
OL,18,FThe 67-year-old died at the scene.
