OL,3,CCompany fined more than #430,000 over
OL,4,Cforklift truck death
OL,6,FAn investigation by the Health and
OL,7,FSafety Executive (HSE) found the
OL,8,Fforklift had not been fully inspected
OL,9,Fto ensure it was safe to operate. It
OL,10,Fhad several defects which should have
OL,11,Fbeen identified.
OL,13,FThe company was fined #433,550 and
OL,14,Fordered to pay more than #8,000 in
OL,15,Fcosts.
OL,17,FMr Keegan's widow Dianne described him
OL,18,Fas "a wonderful, kind and generous
OL,19,Fman, who would do anything he could
OL,20,Ffor anyone".
