OL,6,FShe added: "My heart is broken, and I
OL,7,Fwill never get over losing my husband
OL,8,Fin such a horrific way. He never
OL,9,Fdeserved to die in such tragic
OL,10,Fcircumstances."
OL,12,FLeeds Magistrates' Court heard that Mr
OL,13,FKeegan had been asked to return the
OL,14,Fforklift truck to a customer in
OL,15,FSheffield following repair work.
