OL,6,FAs he reversed it onto a trailer, it
OL,7,Ffell from the side of the trailer bed
OL,8,Fand he was thrown from the seat and
OL,9,Fbecame trapped between the chassis of
OL,10,Fthe forklift and a neighbouring
OL,11,Ftrailer.
OL,13,FAlong with defects to the forklift,
OL,14,Fthe HSE also found that many of the
OL,15,Fcompany's employees would rarely wear
OL,16,Fseatbelts when operating forklift
OL,17,Ftrucks.
